# Optional local overrides. Use placeholder or public values only —
# do not commit credentials.

# --- Astro routing ---
# Override the public site URL and base path. Default values come from
# scripts/pages-routing.mjs.
ASTRO_SITE=<public-site-url>
ASTRO_BASE=<base-path>

# --- Spec source root ---
# Where scripts/spec-content.mjs reads upstream Markdown from.
# Resolution order (see docs/architecture.md → "Repos and how they
# relate"):
#   1. SPEC_ROOT_OVERRIDE (this var) — explicit caller intent, wins.
#   2. external/ai-contributor-spec/ submodule, if it has every
#      required source file.
#   3. ../ai-contributor-spec/ sibling checkout — used by consume
#      branches that need spec-repo content not yet pinned in the
#      submodule; prints a warning when picked.
#   4. Submodule path again (assertSpecSource then fails loud).
#
# Set this when working on a consume branch and you want to silence
# the sibling-fallback warning, or when the spec checkout lives
# somewhere other than the sibling path.
# SPEC_ROOT_OVERRIDE=/absolute/path/to/ai-contributor-spec
